title: Seattle Park District Board - Special Meeting - Public Hearing 9/7/22
description:
Agenda: Call to Order, Roll Call, Approval of Agenda; Public Hearing (The Seattle Park District Board will accept public comment on the Mayors Proposed Seattle Park District Cycle 2 Funding Plan (2023  2028). This meeting held at Northgate Community Center.
